item.description: Come bask in the ambiance (and din) of many people making telephone calls from the same place all at the same time. Bring a cell phone if you have one. (We have a couple extra if you don't.) Bring a WiFi-capable laptop if you have one, as we need to look up some of the numbers. We provide the scripts and training. We'll probably keep going till around 8pm, but feel free to come and go as your schedule permits.
item.name: Phone banking in Dorchester
